{"tid":1610230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解次次一有狗就走晒 我話你知原因","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T05:27:39.000Z","uid":302,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2000046ee46b389d960a33c707b61a394b6c3a","tid":1610230,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:44:31.000Z","msg":"第一：最致命既係一班得普通口罩 同冇諗住打過既手足企前線 <br />\n因為對家一放tg 冇豬咀既根本冇得唔走<br />\n但係你地一走 變相產生一種要逃生既恐懼比其他勇武手足 好多勇武手足本身上留低一戰 但比你地推到要跟住走<br />\n<br />\n第二：和理非走 你地一走 會一下子形成人數大落差<br />\n勇武冇左後排人 自然會驚有狗係後邊包圍佢地 所以和理非既作用 係頂住唔比班狗包圍 提供一條逃走路線比佢地<br />\n<br />\n但係如果你地同前線距離太貼 係會頂唔到tg 跟住恐慌性咁走 就會變返第一點 所以 請同前線保持最少10-20米距離 ！"},{"pid":"8b136d1904aa727b66904280e8dd38705df06014","tid":1610230,"uid":302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:45:46.000Z","msg":"唔該手足唔好再一味叫人上前 上前係要full gear既勇武手足 唔係帶個口罩又叫佢地企前頂住自己啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23494cf8d4c39dff1c65b210f0132f916ddcf1e3","tid":1610230,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:47:42.000Z","msg":"正視聽"},{"pid":"a8e71aec25801b1eb71abcee33a86a4ca8b4c419","tid":1610230,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:48:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/klt1300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fklt1300&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=ca8aa7eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/klt1300</a><br />\n九龍塘 罷工 集會<br />\n又一城見"},{"pid":"452484ac4ef14ab21ce220249fc3a2c96d9f3191","tid":1610230,"uid":288027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:50:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b432a21f83aab59065dd14f464b0460799f4b210","tid":1610230,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"定好位 求下大家 三個月喇"},{"pid":"cc5f182813cfcf761ad4e07a80b46eded8dbd71e","tid":1610230,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2