明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=5339348f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bb9302d2a48abb96d8d951489c09bfaf2db050","tid":1610230,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"208ce15e77979e9f3f95f75228a4c97ecf56677d","tid":1610230,"uid":138429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:05:25.000Z","msg":"冇計，你上過前線就知，本能反應黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:10:56.000Z","msg":"長期前線後少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以要咁<br />\n全部手足同我入黎 咪再on99落到場唔知做乜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610113</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7baedd7d8e882336a96eb62e75fc24de9f0e8add","tid":1610230,"uid":201434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0cd53999a0c738b52bab1c9fd7bb9057f4bfc8c","tid":1610230,"uid":24924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"未放tg和理非已經走緊 佢地係驚自己塞住前線既退路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"和理非真係驚自己走得慢會塞住前面，所以成日見到前面啲人向後退就跑，但其實冇野，之後又行翻前"},{"pid":"1427e21e56c9d4cccf1e32518a34d7b5ed85bd54","tid":1610230,"uid":326643,"like":